                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M22 2L11 13M22 2L15 22L11 13M22 2L2 9L11 13" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
